Package: valley
Type: Package
Title: Valley Segmentation, and Peak Detection
Version: 1.0
Date: 2013-08-14
Author: Julien Prados
Maintainer: Julien Prados <julien.prados@unige.ch>
Copyright: 2013, University of Geneva
Description: Efficiently find valleys of a 1D vector or a 2D matrix. A valley
    of a given point, p, is defined has the highest intensity point, v, between
    p and another point having a higher intensity than p. This information may
    be used to perform image segmentation.
License: GPL-3
Depends:
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.4)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
